==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: A book holds a house of gold.
===Proverb===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' shū zhōng zì yŏu huángjīn wū, shu1zhong1zi4you3huang2jin1wu1)
# If you study hard, you will become successful, and be able to afford to buy a big house.

